{"tid":853490,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"1997 VS 2018 經濟發展水平的統計數據 - 睇下回歸前和回歸後的分別","createTime":"2018-10-08T15:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T14:15:07.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a873f58652fde7540f5a420b48c0f9412c363ceb","tid":853490,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"政府統計數據 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp150_tc.jsp?productCode=D5250036\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp150_tc.jsp%3FproductCode%3DD5250036&d=ytmDTuPZ%2BOZK6zjQ98qKEC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3c0888b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp150_tc.jsp?productCode=D5250036</a><br />\n<br />\n1997 = 1997Q1<br />\n2018 = 2018Q2<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1人家庭</strong>住戶中位數收入<br />\n<strong>1997: 10,000<br />\n2018: 8,300</strong><br />\n<br />\n2人家庭住戶中位數收入<br />\n1997: 18,000<br />\n2018: 20,000<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4人家庭</strong>住戶中位數收入<br />\n<strong>1997: 21,500<br />\n2018: 41,500</strong><br />\n<br />\n公屋家庭<br />\n1997: 16,600<br />\n2018: 22,000<br />\n<br />\n私樓家庭<br />\n1997: 25,500<br />\n2018: 45,000<br />\n<br />\n數據得出黎的數據事實<br />\n回歸後，<strong>毒撚越黎越窮</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n回歸後，<strong>非毒撚越黎越富</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1a82f13c8c121349aa023d6ee9db1c2f97487d","tid":853490,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T00:59:33.000Z","msg":"留意一下，1997年經濟數據，係當年金融風暴未爆時得出 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1284bd269725d49746b46c417826499a02c5982f","tid":853490,"uid":12615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會考慮睇埋通漲?<br />\n剩睇呢兩個數字其實冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ecdf4c4